instructions: Place a dinner plate on the table
Place a dinner fork to the left side of the dinner plate that is on the table
Place a salad fork to the left side of the dinner fork
Place a dinner knife to the right side of the dinner plate
Place a salad knife to the right of the dinner knife
Place a soup spoon to the right side of the salad knife
Place the water glass just in front of soup spoon, salad knife and dinner knife.
Place the wine glass to right side of water glass
Place another wine glass to the right side of the first wine glass
Place a coffee cup next to dinner knife, salad knife and soup spoon
Place a plate bread just in front of dinner fork and salad fork
Place a butter knife inside the bread plate
Place a dessert fork in front of dinner table
Place a dessert spoon in front of the dessert fork
Place a napkin in the dinner plate
